(60, 1, 'Home', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;It can be so much fun to decorate your home and to make it cozy and comfortable where you can relax after a long day. At stickers-center you\'ll find wall decorations, for your best home design. And because we deliver right to your door, decorating could not be more fun and easy!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Home', '', ''),
